{"tid":1282030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(抗負能量) 我好想組個跑步團同大家改善一下情緒","createTime":"2019-07-03T12:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T14:15:18.000Z","uid":92200,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c2df6f5209b058850c65845932b68430391c1c8","tid":1282030,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:51:45.000Z","msg":"呢家成個網絡都充斥住負能量，我明白大家都好緊張最近社會嘅事<br />\n但一個人不斷接受同追逐最新資訊，當中又咁多負能量，其實個人情緒會好崩緊<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望大家要<span style=\"color: red;\">平衡一下情緒</span>，起碼<span style=\"color: orange;\">每晚都抽少少時間</span>跑步 令到<span style=\"color: blue;\">個人舒服啲</span><br />\n<br />\n但自己跑可能無咩動力，我地幾個社工想組個跑步團比大家，只要大家想跑步都可以喺個組入面搵巴打絲打組隊<br />\n當然，跑步速度技術唔係重點，只想大家輕鬆跑 傾下計 互相支持同鼓勵大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地幾個可以集中返新界西陪大家，其他區我地盡量抽時間陪大家 或者 大家都可以自組<br />\n<br />\n有咩詳情入黎傾下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跑步好處<br />\n1. 減壓<br />\n2. 改善情緒問題<br />\n3. 強身健體<br />\n4. 識朋友 (至少有我地)<br />\n<br />\n加入TG Group link<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/D8OHoBUguotyj83NiQil4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FD8OHoBUguotyj83NiQil4w&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=49b6ad10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/D8OHoBUguotyj83NiQil4w</a>"},{"pid":"6cf75ec2954d8a6c641326b6c4f43d48f19284a2","tid":1282030,"uid":92200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:53:58.000Z","msg":"我地AC係連仔比我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家放心"},{"pid":"31f9032673a52f01de8852339f420aa90d9e7e5f","tid":1282030,"uid":16846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:54:05.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔開心嘅做下運動，個人開心啲，又可以強身健體下次野餐都熟手啲"},{"pid":"2f15d5f5963bd721f920f7ec7d3159d6e2522923","tid":1282030,"uid":922